<% end %>
<% set_meta_tags :title => 'Sign up : Grapevine' %>
<div id="main-container" class="clearfix">
<section class="subpage">
  <header>
    <h2 class="title">For people serious about <br />customer reviews and service.</h2>
    <p class="description">Starting Out Doesn't Mean Missing Out. Get up to 5 monthly alerts starting now. <br /> <!-- go to hell josh, that's a break i just put in there -->Upgrade when your business grows to track unlimited reviews or add more business locations to track. <br /><!-- 'nother one there, nah nah -->We'll track all the major review sites for you 24x7 so you don't have to, plus you'll be notified daily.</p>
